videos.description: Jared Harper sends a nice pass up to Anfernee McLemore finishes at the rim with a powerful oop against South Alabama.
videos.headline: Harper lobs it up to McLemore for Auburn oop

videos.description: Samir Doughty rushes to the other end of the court and takes a long feed from Jared Harper before finishing with a layup.
videos.headline: Doughty's layup caps off Auburn's 15-0 run

videos.description: Anfernee McLemore takes the nifty dish from Chuma Okeke and throws it down over South Alabama.
videos.headline: McLemore is there for the jam

videos.description: Chuma Okeke comes up clutch, cleaning up his teammates' miss with a tough layup in the second half.
videos.headline: Okeke lays in acrobatic bucket for Auburn
